{"tid":143461,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"對上一次鍾意人係幾時","createTime":"2017-03-04T15:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T22:23:15.000Z","uid":18867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cbe92649cef9b8c859d54bccbbd5461e5c6615d0","tid":143461,"uid":18867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:42:15.000Z","msg":"對上一次鍾意人已經係高中 <br />\n打後6年無再對女仔動心過 <br />\n<br />\n好想記起當初完全自制唔到想望佢/搵佢既感覺 <br />\n<br />\n好想記起被佢暗示拒絕之後左種酸澀 後悔所做既一切同花左3年鍾意人 <br />\n<br />\n自卑 害怕重蹈覆轍 擔心比唔到佢所期望 我諗就係我一直無主動識女仔既原因 但每次我老母問起點解唔去識 我都講唔出口"},{"pid":"156a11140ab2ca371ab8ef36b7bcbc196360bf9f","tid":143461,"uid":66936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:43:14.000Z","msg":"中途轉機"},{"pid":"255722840c8428d44a35b980a8dc38713053e177","tid":143461,"uid":47590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:49:40.000Z","msg":"岩岩好鍾意一個男仔<br />\n佢應該有鍾意過我但已經頓成往事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a1c477f1b29d11c625829e84e0838786638753","tid":143461,"uid":18867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T15:58:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩好鍾意一個男仔<br />\n佢應該有鍾意過我但已經頓成往事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n假如男仔係我 而我未有女朋友 你仲有機會 因為毒撚超容易動情"},{"pid":"8c85dcfb58787c4262bfce28a23051909ea9f390","tid":143461,"uid":56368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:03:28.000Z","msg":"有無人無鐘意過人<br />\n男女都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806b2d785049d37732ca05ac011155ffef598403","tid":143461,"uid":55190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:10:00.000Z","msg":"鐘意到個女仔連發夢先見到佢<br />\n可惜唔會再有機會再見佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a7102bedc35adbddd9092ca08785a603a0ac968","tid":143461,"uid":55190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:10:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鐘意到個女仔連發夢都見到佢<br />\n可惜唔會再有機會再見佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a73408b60fac43d9230e2bd9221dc7860dc9ad2e","tid":143461,"uid":22222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:13:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鐘意到個女仔連發夢都見到佢<br />\n可惜唔會再有機會再見佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n巴打同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一直喺度諗如果我喺最後一次見佢嗰陣表白會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明大家都好接近 可能就係差嗰一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08fa064ecfba94665420bf5c9e8dedc609e190c8","tid":143461,"uid":47590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:18:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩好鍾意一個男仔<br />\n佢應該有鍾意過我但已經頓成往事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n假如男仔係我 而我未有女朋友 你仲有機會 因為毒撚超容易動情</blockquote><br />\n我咁易就鍾意左個男仔唔通我都係毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我既身份好尷尬可能因為咁而同佢錯失機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33eb00c7d96429e0fd08cd173f732498bd5fa2ef","tid":143461,"uid":6951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:22:37.000Z","msg":"same here<br />\n對上一次鍾意既人係初戀<br />\n分左手5年黎都未鍾意過其他女仔<br />\n唔係放唔低，係唔知點樣開始新感情"},{"pid":"ab7bf3ed0ecbe167a60c170e029497cb24f4f939","tid":143461,"uid":18867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T16:34:57.000Z","msg":"我想試下鍾意人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a862068588304780db433f829b5b7fed0d8929a7","tid":143461,"uid":13873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T17:27:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩好鍾意一個男仔<br />\n佢應該有鍾意過我但已經頓成往事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同我好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但已經過左去了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33361fd3aefa095227f9a500157e958ee784ecc0","tid":143461,"uid":50870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T18:43:38.000Z","msg":"其實中學畢左業就好難 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c2cd443fd08839bccbe96a0e47c9570a2d638b","tid":143461,"uid":70763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T21:44:48.000Z","msg":"三年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0bd78b1534b88aceacb631d11da7f1150769a3","tid":143461,"uid":3162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T22:10:41.000Z","msg":"已經搵唔返種感覺<br />\n就算身邊有啲唔錯嘅<br />\n但真係好耐無試過鍾意人<br />\n但已經放低咗之前鍾意嗰個人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8cb5cdda3e11647e4a8240abcacba49fc24e77","tid":143461,"uid":10399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T22:17:15.000Z","msg":"5年前"},{"pid":"1ee0a89c91bbd81cae4bad555a52a76e94381f15","tid":143461,"uid":83557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T22:23:15.000Z","msg":"3年前"}]}